wikipedia_page.main: Andrew Robert Isaac Umeed (born 19 April 1996) is a Scottish first-class cricketer. He made his first-class debut in the 2015–17 ICC Intercontinental Cup against Afghanistan in June 2015. He made his List A debut for Warwickshire against the West Indies A team in a tri-series warm-up match on 17 June 2018.
